                     add   1              to   w-exe-sel-pro
           else      move  "N"            to   srt-sel-pro            .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice prodotto senza barcode           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcp-klb    =    spaces
                     move  "N"            to   srt-snb-pro
           else      move  "S"            to   srt-snb-pro            .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Un intero record [bfr]                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bfr               to   srt-rec-bfr            .
       exe-cph-lv1-inp-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Rilascio del record al Sort                     *
